attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a rolling cart. The student starts by screwing the side bars onto the cart, then the base frame. Next, the student attaches the legs and screws the bottom tray onto the side bars. The student repeats this process for the middle and top tray. Finally, the student places the wheels on the cart and tighten them with a wrench.
